title: Jani Hartikainen
text: Jani Hartikainen (born 16 September 1975) is a <a href="Finland">Finnish</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player who currently plays for the <a href="Finland">Finnish</a> premiership <a href="Veikkausliiga">Veikkausliiga</a> club <a href="KuPS">KuPS</a> in <a href="Finland">Finland</a>.
